Joburg Mayor Geoff Makhubo has passed away due to COVID-19 complications. He was recently hospitalised with the virus. Makhubo was elected mayor in 2019. For reaction, eNCA's Dan Moyane speaks to ANC Regional Spokesperson, Sasabona Manganye. Courtesy #DStv403 JOHANNESBURG - Tributes have poured in for Johannesburg mayor Geoff Makhubo. Makhubo has passed away due to COVID-19 complications. He was recently hospitalised with the virus. READ: Tributes pour in for Jabu Mabuza Makhubo was elected mayor in 2019. ANC Regional spokesperson, Sasabona Manganye says Makhubo's passing has left a big gap.